# Host paths or docker volumes to mount into the sandbox so caches and
# credentials survive runs.
#
# Syntax (one per line; `#` comments and blanks ignored):
#   <host_rel>                            host bind, container = /home/dev/<host_rel>
#   <host_rel>:<container_path>           host bind, explicit container path
#   @<volume_name>:<container_path>       named docker volume (auto-tracked by clean/purge)
.npm
.cache/yarn                              # yarn berry; harmless if you don't use yarn
.local/share/pnpm/store                  # pnpm; harmless if you don't use pnpm
